---
import { ROUTES } from '@data/routes';
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="Full affiliate disclosure for chill-dogs. Transparency about how we earn revenue.">
  <section class="legal container">
    <div class="prose">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

      <p>
        chill-dogs is a participant in the <strong>Amazon Services LLC Associates Program</strong>, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
      </p>

      <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
      <p>
        When you click on a product link on our site and make a purchase on Amazon, we may receive a small commission. This comes at <strong>no additional cost to you</strong> — the price you pay is exactly the same whether you use our link or go directly to Amazon.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Commitment to Honesty</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate commissions never influence our product recommendations. We only recommend products we have thoroughly researched and genuinely believe will benefit you and your dog. If a product isn't worth your money, we won't recommend it — regardless of the commission.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Make Money</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate commissions are the primary way we fund this website. This revenue allows us to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Maintain and host this website</li>
        <li>Research and compare products</li>
        <li>Create free, helpful content for dog parents</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Identifying Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate links on our site are typically "Check Price on Amazon" or "View on Amazon" buttons. We also include disclosure notices near affiliate content throughout the site.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships, please <a href={ROUTES.contact}>contact us</a>. We believe in full transparency and are happy to answer any questions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding-top: var(--space-3xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .legal h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
</style>
